msgstr "You can find the settings for <strong><a href=\"https://kursadmin.kursagenten.no/ProviderInformation\" target=\"_blank\">Provider ID and Provider GUID</a></strong> in Kursagenten under <em>Company information -> Settings</em>, and <strong><a href=\"https://kursadmin.kursagenten.no/IframeSetting\" target=\"_blank\">Theme for course lists</a></strong> under <em>Embedded / iframe</em><br><br>In Integration settings, under the <strong><a href=\"https://kursadmin.kursagenten.no/IntegrationSettings\" target=\"_blank\">Webhooks</a></strong> tab, enter %s in the CourseCreated and CourseUpdated fields to automatically update courses when they are created or changed in Kursagenten."

